00:05:31,669 --> 00:05:34,269
Terima kasih sudah berkunjung ke sini.

68
00:05:34,269 --> 00:05:36,369
"Sogen Nakatani (54)" -Aku Nakatani, wali kota.

69
00:05:36,369 --> 00:05:40,469
Mari lakukan wawancaranya setelah tur.

