161
00:10:34,469 --> 00:10:37,369
Kau baik-baik saja?

162
00:10:37,369 --> 00:10:38,669
Bau ini...

163
00:10:38,669 --> 00:10:40,169
Yoshida, mundur!

164
00:10:56,969 --> 00:10:58,069
Ayumi, ada apa?

165
00:10:59,069 --> 00:11:00,769
