167
00:11:06,769 --> 00:11:07,969
Bau ini...

168
00:11:30,436 --> 00:11:31,436
"Misao Yamamura"

169
00:11:31,436 --> 00:11:33,536
"Inspektur Polisi Divisi 1 Prefektur Gunma" -Oh, begitu ya.

170
00:11:33,536 --> 00:11:37,536
