173
00:11:43,436 --> 00:11:45,536
Apa itu benar?

174
00:11:45,536 --> 00:11:48,436
Ya, benar.

175
00:11:48,436 --> 00:11:51,736
Korban tidak memakan atau meminum apapun

176
