184
00:12:18,036 --> 00:12:21,136
Apa? Benar katamu.

185
00:12:25,136 --> 00:12:27,336
Wah, Conan lagi rupanya.

186
00:12:27,336 --> 00:12:28,736
Apa Pak Mouri

