00:12:40,736 --> 00:12:44,036
Permisi, tapi aku rasa ini bukan kasus kriminal.

192
00:12:44,036 --> 00:12:45,536
Apa? Kau siapa?

193
00:12:45,536 --> 00:12:47,336
Nakatani, walikota.

