199
00:13:02,836 --> 00:13:03,836
Kenapa?

200
00:13:03,836 --> 00:13:05,736
Aku tidak pasti.

201
00:13:05,736 --> 00:13:10,336
Mungkin karena tetesan bulan.

202
00:13:11,936 --> 00:13:14,336
Apa itu tetesan bulan?

203
00:13:14,336 --> 00:13:16,736
Itu fosil langka yang terbuat dari cangkang.

204
00:13:16,736 --> 00:13:18,236
Begitu, ya.

205
00:13:18,236 --> 00:13:20,036
Sebenarnya

206
00:13:20,036 --> 00:13:23,336
